<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <style>
        .about-couple-photo {
            width: 130%;
            max-width: 130%;
            margin-left: -180px;
        }

        .about-couple-text {
            padding-left: 48px;
        }

        .smoker-progression {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 28px 24px;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .smoker-step {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .smoker-step img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: 260px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .smoker-step h4 {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 991px) {
            .about-couple-photo {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 100%;
                margin-left: 0;
            }

            .about-couple-text {
                padding-left: 15px;
            }

            .smoker-progression {
                max-width: 100%;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .smoker-progression {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .smoker-step img {
                height: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body id="page-top" class="regular-navigation">
    <%- include('partials/gtm-noscript') %>
    <div class="master-wrapper">

        <%- include('partials/nav') %>

        <section class="light-wrapper">
            <div class="section-inner">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row mb50">
                        <br>

                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Landon and Aspyn.jpeg" alt="Landon and Aspyn" class="img-responsive about-couple-photo" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-6 about-couple-text">
                            <h2 class="section-heading">Landon and <span class="theme-accent-color">Aspyn</span></h2>
                            <p class="lead">We’re the people behind Lando’s BBQ. We have a deep passion for good food, quality,
                                 and standing proudly behind everything we serve. For us, BBQ isn’t just about what’s on the plate, it’s about the care, time,
                                  and intention that go into making something worth sharing. We love seeing the smiles around the table and knowing our food played a
                                   small part in bringing people together. BBQ is more than food. It’s about connection, slowing down, and creating moments people remember.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row text-center mb30">
                        <div class="col-lg-12">
                            <h3 class="section-heading">Our Story</h3>
                            <hr class="thin-hr">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row mb50">
                        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
                            <p class="lead">From our first backyard cooks to full trailer setups, every smoker taught us something new. This journey shaped the flavor, process, and consistency behind every plate we serve.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                                      <div class="smoker-progression">
                        <div class="smoker-step">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Traeger.jpeg" alt="Traeger smoker" class="img-responsive" />
                            <!-- <h4>Traeger</h4> -->
                        </div>

                        <div class="smoker-step">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Offset.jpeg" alt="Offset smoker" class="img-responsive" />
                            <!-- <h4>Offset</h4> -->
                        </div>

                        <div class="smoker-step">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Brazos.jpeg" alt="Brazos smoker" class="img-responsive" />
                            <!-- <h4>Brazos</h4> -->
                        </div>

                        <div class="smoker-step">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Goldees Smoker.jpeg" alt="Goldees smoker" class="img-responsive" />
                            <!-- <h4>Goldees Smoker</h4> -->
                        </div>

                        <div class="smoker-step">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Trailer Smoker in Garage.jpeg" alt="Trailer smoker in garage" class="img-responsive" />
                            <!-- <h4>Trailer Smoker in Garage</h4> -->
                        </div>

                        <div class="smoker-step">
                            <img src="/assets/img/Trailer Smoker.jpeg" alt="Trailer smoker" class="img-responsive" />
                            <!-- <h4>Trailer Smoker</h4> -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    </div>

    <%- include('partials/scripts') %>

</body>

</html>
